name: Billy the Exterminator
overview: Follow Billy Bretherton and his family of exterminators as they attempt to balance life at home with the drama of running one of the busiest pest removal companies in Louisiana. From colonies of ants to giant snakes, snapping alligators to roach infestations, pest removal is big business, and in the swamps of Louisiana, Billy the Exterminator has seen it all.

seasons.name: Season 7
seasons.overview: Exterminator Billy Bretherton leaves Louisiana behind and brings his skills to the wilds of the Great White North.

episodes.name: Snake in the Closet.
episodes.overview: A sports stadium with a bat problem is tackled. Also: a vacant house filled with mice and an enormous snake.

episodes.name: There's a Gator in My Boat
episodes.overview: Billy travels to a farm to snag an alligator, which ends up taking a bite out of him. Later, Billy and Rick tackle a swarm of wasps at a home.

episodes.name: Possums in the Wall
episodes.overview: Billy battles termites in a house that is going up for sale. Later, he travels to a home where a family of possums are living in the walls.

episodes.name: Llama-Eating Gators
episodes.overview: Billy goes after an alligator who poses a threat to pet llamas on a ranch.

episodes.name: Psycho Racoon / Killer Spiders
episodes.overview: An unidentified creature is living in the walls of a home; and black widows infest a family's house.

episodes.name: Racoon Hunting
episodes.overview: A raccoon problem at a plantation leads to the discovery of an enormous mound of raccoon excrement in an attic. Also: a wasp infestation in the home of a deaf couple.

episodes.name: Skunks and Mice and Snakes Oh My
Funeral Home Snake
episodes.overview: The dead aren't resting peacefully at this funeral home because a rattlesnake is loose in the crematorium. Billy and Ricky search for the snake, but it finds them first--and it's a mean one! Later, Billy heads into a treacherous attic to deal with some bats, knowing that one false step could send him plunging through the floor.

episodes.name: Attack of the Trash Can Raccoon
episodes.overview: It's Billy vs. the Raccoon when the feisty animal gets trapped in a dumpster--and Billy knows it won't give up without a big fight. Later, Billy's got another tough battle on his hands when he comes up against some Cicada Killer Wasps with their very painful stingers.

episodes.name: Snake Invader
episodes.overview: Armadillos, and snakes, and roaches, oh, my. When Billy and Ricky get a call about an armadillo terrorizing a woman's garden, they arrive to discover that a poisonous snake may be on the loose, too. Later, Billy confronts one of the biggest roach infestations of his career in the home of a client with severe health issues. Meanwhile, back at the office, Mary's trying to give orders--and she doesn't even work there!

episodes.name: Raccoon Rescue
episodes.overview: The crew must help a raccoon that's stuck in a tree with a peanut-butter jar on its head; and Billy climbs a theater catwalk to capture pigeons with his bare hands.

episodes.name: Spider Invasion
episodes.overview: Billy hunts for a nutria in his mother's neighbor's yard; and Billy and Ricky tackle a cabin full of poisonous brown recluse spiders.

episodes.name: Squirrels in the Attic
episodes.overview: Billy and Rick handle a wasp infestation; and Billy tries to catch a squirrel in an attic and discovers a fire hazard.

episodes.name: Squirrel Gone Wild
episodes.overview: Billy retrieves a dead animal beneath a home; and Billy and Rick try to catch a squirrel that's loose in a house.

episodes.name: Sprayed by a Skunk!
episodes.overview: Billy hunts an alligator living in a pond at a golf club; and tries to catch a skunk that's a threat to a couple's young daughter.

episodes.name: Python on the Prowl
episodes.overview: Billy and Rick deal with a yellow jacket nest that's five times the size of a normal nest; and Billy must get a rid of a python living in a home.

episodes.name: Billy Goes to the Gulf
episodes.overview: In this special one-hour episode, Billy and his brother Ricky travel to the Gulf Coast and find themselves head-to-head with the devastation caused by the Deepwater Horizon oil spill. Along the way they battle a pair of foxes, help a local charity deal with a massive roach infestation, and witness first-hand the effects the oil is having on wildlife.

episodes.name: Coffin of Deadly Reptiles
episodes.overview: In the third-season opener, the brothers remove an alligator stuck in a duck blind with two venomous snakes, as well as crayfish and roaches.

episodes.name: Fox Fight!
episodes.overview: Billy searches for a fox that poses a threat to a mother and her child;  and a swarm of yellow jackets have left a family's bathroom unusable.

episodes.name: Snakes in a Pool
episodes.overview: Billy tries to catch snakes at the bottom of a pool that's nearly empty and very slippery; and helps a rancher who's battling a beaver.

episodes.name: Bees from Hell
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky battle a swarm of bees at a Baptist church; and Billy encounters an animal he's never dealt with before.

episodes.name: Five Alarm Hive
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky rescue firefighter trainees from bees swarming a fire-department training center.

episodes.name: Raccoon Rampage
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky battle raccoons that are stealing expensive kangaroo food at a petting zoo; and Billy tackles a roach infestation.

episodes.name: Monster Mice
episodes.overview: Billy is attacked by wasps; and Billy and Ricky help a single mother who has a mouse problem.

episodes.name: Hogs Gone Wild!
episodes.overview: The men battle feral hogs, and experts are called in to help; and Billy and Ricky rescue an injured baby bunny.

episodes.name: When Gators Attack
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky are in Texas, working with local gator experts, to catch an aggressive gator hidden in a family's back yard. Billy grabs it by the tail and it starts striking at everything that moves. When the gator bites one of the men's arms, everyone present works towards catching it before it can attack anyone else.

episodes.name: Desert Destroyers
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky head to Phoenix, Arizona where they face off against a herd of teeth chomping Javelina that are terrorizing a family. Then, a close call with one of the deadliest desert dwellers leaves them a bit rattled. It's about to get western!

episodes.name: What Lurks Beneath
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky travel to Beaumont, Texas where they wrangle two giant gators, one of which is hiding in the back yard of a family with small children. Then they're off to Miami, Florida to help with a massive infestation of bed bugs that is literally eating the client alive.

episodes.name: Furry Infestation
episodes.overview: Things get out of hand in Chicago when Billy is attacked and bitten by several squirrels squatting in a homeowner's living room.

episodes.name: Aerial Attack
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky head to Charlotte, North Carolina where they find out just how vicious geese can be when you mess with their nests. Using only an umbrella for cover, Billy defends himself from a nasty aerial assault by two very angry birds.

episodes.name: Bobcat Battle
episodes.overview: Billy and his brother Ricky receive a little help from an old friend while battling a bobcat. And the extra hand comes in handy when a scaly surprise comes their way during the course of the job.

episodes.name: Suck It Up
episodes.overview: Billy and his brother Ricky travel to Miami. But it's not all surf and sun--after capturing an angry snake that's invaded a home, they're faced with relocating a massive bee hive threatening a family.

episodes.name: Dirty Rat
episodes.overview: A local bank calls Billy to make an arrest when they discover a dirty rat making illegal withdrawals overnight. The clever criminal is caught on tape but Billy shows them it's not their money he's after, it's something much more valuable to this Ratty Hearst! Later, Billy and Ricky battle to save a dying kitten stuck in a wall.

episodes.name: Good Morning Gators
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky are on the job in Savannah, Georgia with some high profile visitors. Good Morning America joins them to get a taste of the unpredictable job of trapping gators! America is watching as Billy and Ricky are in hot pursuit of multiple gators lurking in a local children's park.

episodes.name: Skunks on a Plane
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky go to the local water park and Billy takes a sudden dip to save a life when a desperate critter plunges into the lazy river. Later Ricky dances with danger as he faces off with a skunk in an airplane hangar.

episodes.name: Hoarder House Rats
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky are called out to one of their grossest jobs yet; a hoarder house full of rats! The good news is that the house is going to be demolished so the Bretherton brothers swing a few axes as they set the bait. The bad news is that they have to collect some nasty decomposing rats in the Louisiana heat.

episodes.name: Gators in Waiting
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky head to Savannah, Georgia to round up some gators moving in on the local ATV Park. The boys have their work cut out for them when an eight-foot gator just won't cooperate.

episodes.name: Python Power
episodes.overview: It's all about snakes in this episode. Billy has to trap a deadly rattlesnake in a family's backyard and then finds himself wrestling with a 15-foot python that wraps itself around his neck.

episodes.name: Aggravated Assault
episodes.overview: Aggressive bees that Billy suspects are Africanized sting him repeatedly while he's trying to remove a hive up high on a column in a New Orleans neighborhood. The homeowner is allergic but one of the tenants dresses up to make sure the bees are removed unharmed so Billy has his work cut out for him.

episodes.name: Mission Impossible
episodes.overview: Billy is called to a homeless shelter in New Orleans with a massive rat infestation that nobody can solve. If Billy doesn't get to the bottom of it they will be forced to close. When his bait keeps disappearing Billy realizes that another disgusting pest has been sabotaging him and doubles his efforts to stamp them out.

episodes.name: Swarm of the Angry Bees
episodes.overview: A desperate family asks Billy to help them with an aggressive bee colony that has taken over their entire house. Billy takes multiple stings and for the first time ever has to run from the bees to avoid being swarmed.

episodes.name: Giant Rats in the City
episodes.overview: Billy is called out to Chicago to deal with a nasty rat infestation in a downtown apartment basement. Listen to them squeal when he catches some by hand trying to creep around him in the dark. The squealing continues when Billy helps rescue a fat squirrel stuck in a suburban household pipe the next day.

episodes.name: Predator in the Pond
episodes.overview: A feisty gator proves to be a worthy opponent for Billy as he's learning how to hand capture gators. Later, he and Ricky help to rescue a 14-foot albino python that they come across in the middle of the road.

episodes.name: Backyard Swarm
episodes.overview: Billy is called to save a family under siege from critters. With a raccoon that's behaving badly around the kids and a giant beehive next to the playhouse, the family backyard has become a nest of horrors--and it's up to Billy to save them.

episodes.name: Vampires and Serpents
episodes.overview: Billy is in Baton Rouge battling a huge bat colony that has taken over a homeowner's attic. Then he gets an emergency call about a ten-foot reticulated python hanging out in a family's' pool. He jumps in to grab it and finds himself in an unexpected underwater struggle.

episodes.name: Night of the Living Possums
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky visit the most terrifying spot in New Orleans, and run into some nasty critters that have been terrorizing the demons and ghouls. It's a race against time as they strive to save the undead from the living!

episodes.name: Swamp Monster
episodes.overview: Billy is called out to battle a giant alligator that's eating everything in a lake--and eyeing the family dog for desert! Later, Billy and Big Bill are called out to handle an emergency raccoon that's trapped at a local business.

episodes.name: Roadkill
episodes.overview: Billy tears it up on the racecourse when he sets some traps for some unwanted speed bumps on the track. Big Bill takes a high speed spin but gets a sharp wake up call from Miss Donnie when his heart monitor goes off and Billy is shocked by what he finds in his trap.

episodes.name: Snake, Rattle and Roll
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky are on their toes, as they risk a painful demise in one of the gnarliest snake jobs ever! A house full of pit vipers, where a single wrong move could mean a lethal bite, threatens to take the guys down.

episodes.name: Monster in the Gulf
episodes.overview: Chivalry is not dead as a damsel in distress pulls over her ant-infested car and enlists Billy s help with this invasive crawling menace.

episodes.name: Monsters in the Closet
episodes.overview: Billy doesn't know what he'll find when he's called to save three young girls from "a monster" in their bedroom. Then it's off to Texas to team up with Gator Gary and field test a brand new alligator trap

episodes.name: Raccoon Cage Match
episodes.overview: Billy gets caught in a cage match with an angry mama raccoon at a rehabilitation center before an emergency call out with Ricky to battle a massive potentially lethal beehive that has taken over a family s backyard.

episodes.name: Fight or Flight
episodes.overview: Billy and Ricky must balance atop a Baptist church as they battle a beehive consuming the brick column behind the church's wooden cross.

episodes.name: Wasp Warfare
episodes.overview: Billy goes up against two of the worst insect infestations he's ever seen - red wasps and pine beetles. Meanwhile, with Vexcon stretching at the seams, the Bretherton family hires a new hand - Cousin Chris.

episodes.name: Catch 'Em If You Can
episodes.overview: Billy takes on Vexcon s first ever donkey job and it's a wild ride for Ricky and Billy as the brothers are run ragged by these wily creatures. Eventually they must resort to a tranquilizer gun and get down to business. Later, Billy takes on a master escape artist, a loose rooster so quick and clever it takes three of Vexcon s best to take him down.

episodes.name: Claws and Jaws
episodes.overview: Billy is called to catch a tenacious red fox trapped in a family playroom. Then Billy and Ricky kick it into double-time, as they are called to extract an enormous alligator turtle that threatens a property full of workers and children.

episodes.name: Razor Sharp & Angry
episodes.overview: Billy launches a full assault to save a Marine veteran's home from a bat invasion. Then things get sticky when Billy takes a call for two stubborn and aggressive porcupines who have taken over a woman's backyard.

episodes.name: Feathers & Fangs
episodes.overview: Billy launches a full assault to save a Marine veteran's home from a bat invasion. Then things get sticky when Billy takes a call for two stubborn and aggressive porcupines who have taken over a woman's backyard.

episodes.name: Roach Riot
episodes.overview: Time to get down and dirty when Billy takes on one of the grossest cockroach infestation he has ever seen!

episodes.name: The Big Freeze
episodes.overview: Billy gets a call from a fencing school which is being threatened by a colony of rats. With rats hiding in every nook and cranny to pursue, he must come up with a plan to lure them out.

episodes.name: Monster Maze
episodes.overview: A haunted children s maze can t re-open until Billy clears away the many dangerous creepy crawlies that lurk behind every corner.

episodes.name: Snarl Slither & Snap
episodes.overview: Billy spends the night on a stakeout for a menacing red fox which threatens the animals at a local rehabilitation center. Then, in the light of day, things really heat up when Billy and Cousin Chris find countless water moccasins on a young family's property.

episodes.name: Gator Pool Party
episodes.overview: Billy gets wet and has to get in the deep end of a pool to remove an aggressive gator from a backyard pool, but grabbing the reptile with his bare hands, is easier said than done. Before he can say catch pole, he s off to corral a gang of raccoons who have taken over a local skate park.

episodes.name: Traps and Snaps
episodes.overview: It's a first for Billy when he s called out to remove a South American Coatimundi terrorizing a woman s property. But this critter s ferocious and witty nature keeps Billy at a distance.

episodes.name: Canine Cage Match
episodes.overview: A new mother calls Billy after a wild canine snatches her dog and is hunting her other pets. When Billy's trap is too small for the job, he suits up and throws down in a no holds barred cage match with one of the North's most feared predators. Early spring brings a baby boom, as critters get busy in attics and garages. Billy then teams up with trapper Ben for a dawn to dusk eviction of ferocious squatters who won't go without a fight.

episodes.name: Henhouse of Horrors
episodes.overview: Billy stakes out a northern farm where a predator is creating a horror show at a chicken coop. Later: he goes north to help remove a group of beavers who dammed up a creek and washed out the local road.

episodes.name: Snakes on a Boat
episodes.overview: Billy heads to cottage country where a houseboat rental company finds a nest of snakes inside one of their boats. Billy and his exterminator partner Derick jump into the serpent moshpit and attempt to break up the slithering party.

episodes.name: Paranormal Extermination
episodes.overview: Billy responds to a construction site where a vicious varmint has the tradespeople running scared. He tries to outsmart the beast, and takes some brutal bites in the process. And strange paranormal activity jeopardizes the sale of a country home, so Billy enlists his reluctant dispatcher Bea to investigate. They go in prepared for a ghost hunt, and get more than they bargained for.

episodes.name: Wild Wedding Party
episodes.overview: With a gang of wild turkeys tearing apart a country wedding venue, a stressed-out wedding planner calls on Billy to puts the bride's big day back on track. But the birds prove to be more agile than anticipated. What ensues is a comedy of errors as Billy and his partner, Terry, try to put this poultry in its place! Then a trio of Vietnamese Centipedes with a nasty nature and a serious bite is on the loose in a basement apartment! Billy puts himself in the line of fire to keep a family safe.

episodes.name: Sting Operation
episodes.overview: Billy gets a call from a terrified family with three young children. There's a honey bee nest inside their house! Billy calls on his buddy Ian, a local beekeeper, to help him move the angry bees to a happy place, but the colony doesn't go quietly. Billy suffers a few stings while struggling to get the upper hand. Then Billy has to dodge talons and beak to hand-catch a Great Horned Owl that's stuck in a family's rural home.

episodes.name: Reptile Rampage
episodes.overview: Billy gets called to a quiet suburban neighborhood where an unassuming home has been converted into a reptile rooming house. The dangerous rescue mission requires Billy to wrestle crocs, serpents and lizards and hand them over to a sanctuary. Then, further up north, Billy gets help from local trapper, Mike, to take charge of a couple of prickly porcupine cottage-squatters that need to get gone!

episodes.name: I Smell a Rat Infestation
episodes.overview: Billy is asked to round up a group of ostriches that escaped from a farm. Also: first-time house flippers call on Billy to eradicate a severe rat infestation in their home.

episodes.name: Later, Alligator
episodes.overview: A reptile invades a nature lover's pool and Billy is called in to try and remove it. Later: he tackles an apartment home infested with bedbugs.

episodes.name: Magic Show Mayhem
episodes.overview: Billy helps a magician after his animals run amok during a show at a retirement home. Later: he visits a maple syrup-maker who is plagued by a skunk.

episodes.name: Horns Up
episodes.overview: A prank gets out of hand when fraternity brothers get a goat in their house and Billy is tasked with removing it. Later: Billy faces flying squirrels that have invaded a family's attic.

7.name: Season 7
7.overview: Exterminator Billy Bretherton leaves Louisiana behind and brings his skills to the wilds of the Great White North.
